graph LR
    ModelRegistryOp[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelRegistryOp -->|ML Metadata storage<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 TLS| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+<br/>Required]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|Alternative storage<br/>MySQL/3306 TLS| MySQL[MySQL 5.7+<br/>Alternative to PostgreSQL]

    %% External Dependencies (OpenShift)
    ModelRegistryOp -->|TLS certificates<br/>Auto-rotation| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Optional]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|User authentication<br/>HTTPS/443| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>Optional for OAuth mode]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|External exposure<br/>Routes| IngressRouter[OpenShift Ingress Router<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|Platform integration<br/>CR Watch| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator /<br/>rhods-operator]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|Container image<br/>Deployment| ModelRegistryService[odh-model-registry<br/>REST API service]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|Metrics scraping<br/>HTTPS/8443| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]

    %% Kubernetes Core Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|Reconciliation<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Required]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    KServe[KServe] -.->|Fetches model metadata<br/>REST API| ModelRegistryOp
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management<br/>REST API| ModelRegistryOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|Model registration<br/>REST API| ModelRegistryOp

    %% External Image Dependencies
    OAuthProxyImage[quay.io/openshift/<br/>origin-oauth-proxy:latest] -.->|Sidecar image| ModelRegistryOp
    RegistryImage[quay.io/opendatahub/<br/>model-registry:latest] -.->|Service image| ModelRegistryService

